title: The Devonshire

posting_body: ['Welcome home to luxury living in Boston.', ' Enjoy stainless steel kitchen appliances by Fisher & Paykel, new kitchen lighting, backsplashes and countertops.', 'These apartments have new hard wood flooring throughout.', 'Bathrooms are updated with new plumbing fixtures, white quartz counters, and highend backsplash and tiles.', ' Enjoy the convenience of in-unit washer and dryer.', 'Call today for a tour and get to experiencing life  from a whole new skyline view that is defined by luxury and bliss.', "Situated in the heart of Bean Town's best neighborhoods.", ' Conveniently located minutes from everything that the Bostonian Heart desires.... shopping, dining, famous cultural landmarks, Quincy Market, Faneuil Hall, Boston Commons,  the Seaport District, Public Gardens and the North End.', " Within minutes from multiple lines of transportation, South Station, North Station, and Boston's Logan Airport.", 'The building features amazing amenities that creates a living experience of true luxury.', 'Amazing premier service options are available to level up your lifestyle.', "Relax in the Skyclub leisure room, excercise in the pool or Yoga studio and take in with breathtaking views of Boston's skyline.", 'There is valet parking, 24 hour concierge service, housekeeping, laundry and drycleaning services, package delivery notification servicee, bike storage, and guest suites for out of town visitors.', 'Residents can work, relax, socialize, exercise or swim with magnificent views of the city and harbor as the backdrop.', 'Nicole Fannoney (Realtor, eXp  Realty LLC)', '(781) 607-4118', 'Spreading Joy from one door to the next!']
